<p>Dave has a MacBook Pro tale of woe to tell, then it&rsquo;s off to listener questions and tips. Today&rsquo;s topics include updating an unconnected Mac, sending mail from alternate addresses through Gmail, a question about hiding your IP address, and more!</p>
<p>Note: Shownotes are complete!</p>
